OL,3,CLeading WASPI campaigner's 10 year
OL,4,Cfight with government for compensation
OL,6,FWomen born in the 1950s like Mrs
OL,7,FMadden have been pushing for
OL,8,Fcompensation after the pension age was
OL,9,Fextended beyond the age of 60 while
OL,10,Fthey were on the cusp of retirement.
OL,12,FThey claim the lack of notice - along
OL,13,Fwith women quitting work earlier to
OL,14,Ffulfil care responsibilities - left
OL,15,Fthem financially out of pocket.
OL,17,F"I expected to retire in June 2014 on
OL,18,Fmy 60th birthday," she told ITV. "In
OL,19,FMarch 2012 I got a letter saying I
OL,20,Fwasn't going to retire until 2020.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
