OL,3,CLeading WASPI campaigner's 10 year
OL,4,Cfight with government for compensation
OL,6,F"I was incensed - so I wrote to my
OL,7,Flocal MP and that's what got me into
OL,8,Fthe campaign."
OL,10,FMrs Madden said the prospect of
OL,11,Freturning to work at this time would
OL,12,Fhave been incredibly difficult due to
OL,13,Fher job in IT, in which major
OL,14,Fadvancements had been made while she
OL,15,Fwas out of work.
OL,17,F"The injustice it caused deserves
OL,18,Fcompensation," Mrs Madden said.
