OL,3,CLeading WASPI campaigner's 10 year
OL,4,Cfight with government for compensation
OL,6,F"Women are the child bearers in this
OL,7,Fsociety, they're the carers. We are
OL,8,Foften called the sandwich generation
OL,9,Fbecause we help our children look
OL,10,Fafter their children and we're also
OL,11,Flooking after elderly relatives.
OL,13,F"We saved the state a fortune by
OL,14,Flooking after our own rather than
OL,15,Fhaving to have them looked after by
OL,16,Fthe state and that's not recognised at
OL,17,Fall."
