OL,3,CLeading WASPI campaigner's 10 year
OL,4,Cfight with government for compensation
OL,6,FWork and Pensions Secretary Pat
OL,7,FMcFadden said on Wednesday last week
OL,8,Fit would reconsider compensation for
OL,9,FWASPI women in light of new evidence
OL,10,Femerging in the legal challenge to the
OL,11,Fgovernment's prior refusal.
OL,13,FHe told the Commons: "Retaking this
OL,14,Fdecision should not be taken as an
OL,15,Findication that the government will
OL,16,Fnecessarily decide that it should
OL,17,Faward financial redress.
OL,19,F"The work will begin immediately and I
OL,20,Fwill update the House on the decision
OL,21,Fas soon as a conclusion is reached."
